#ident	"@(#)bkrs:bkintf.d/backups/bkstat/limit/Help	1.2.1.1"

ABSTRACT: Limit Time of Backup Status Log Entries
	The "limit" task allows you to set the length of time (in weeks)
	that entries in the backup status log are kept.  The default is
	the current value.

TITLE: Limit Time of Backup Status Log Entries

F1:Weeks(s) Field
	"Weeks:"  Enter the number of weeks you want status log information
	to be kept.  Entries older than that number of weeks will be
	deleted automatically.  The number you enter must be a whole number
	greater than or equal to 1.
